er m\u00e5ned, en kostnads\u00f8kning p\u00e5 om lag 18 000 kroner p\u00e5 et \u00e5r.", "- Det g\u00e5r. Det handler om \u00e5 prioritere. Hvis det kniper kan jeg innrede en leilighet til, sier Silas O. Skibnes.", "Dyrere l\u00e5n. {ndash} Jeg har \u00f8konomi til \u00e5 klare det, sier Silas O. Skibnes. Med nesten 2,3 millioner kroner i l\u00e5n, risikerer han \u00e5 betale en dr\u00f8y tusenlapp mer i m\u00e5neden, hvis renten fortsetter \u00e5 stige."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "071ed7638506e0d49bdc703973c7f555414413d2ee301d9d61da1581334986de"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-20T07:35:57.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Silas O. Skibnes (25) har 2,3 millioner i husl\u00e5n, men bekymrer seg ikke for rente\u00f8kningen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/67078cfc86fe7ee98952418ef5b978d35d331df7.jpg?5996b7e3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Silas er ikke bekymret -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "67078cfc86fe7ee98952418ef5b978d35d331df7"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "business"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["renten fortsetter", "prosent", "renten", "bank", "l\u00e5n", "m\u00e5ned"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["sparebank 1", "norges bank", "trondheim 200", "kongens"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "midt-norge"}, {"field": "kw-pa